      "type": ["string", "null"],
      "examples": [
        "Foundational Ring 1 anchor entry. Used as universality baseline.",
        "Oral tradition. Written form first recorded by ethnographer in 1962. Source PDF in sources/.",
        "Two translations compared before selecting this wording. Original Pali differs slightly.",
